{"id":"5b2605b8eea72beedad5c55e7f578b374e874b18c81890506c32b19a91b23195","item_id":"19b5d27638:0","text":"可以使用 RenderMan Shelf，或在 shop pane 中创建材质。"}
{"id":"4769190051bd25b97db9354802b54913339bd6e075a8fb9411159103471837c9","item_id":"19b5d27638:1","text":"使用 MAT Pane（MAT 面板）"}
{"id":"6b409743695a8a6aae558bad929ba2f023f430b9d48632b7ae86a8275ac07c98","item_id":"19b5d27638:2","text":"创建 Material：PxrMaterialBuilder。"}
{"id":"8fefe3960f6e44422a454381b237e8f0eec972c586641785474dbf720ff8ad28","item_id":"19b5d27638:3","text":"注意，此节点会过滤掉不受支持的节点"}
{"id":"32c36d60159ae076eb62922ad27349c0dfd8bdfa9405c8244821b4175ef8ea97","item_id":"19b5d27638:4","text":"进入 Material Builder（双击），创建一个 BxDF VOP，即 PxrSurface，并将其连接到 output_collect（如果知道后续会分层效果，建议使用 PxrLayerSurface）"}
{"id":"cd4468295cc7e8b253ae9c82431455ee3c7a4f299acd6914ead596602a4a0b4b","item_id":"19b5d27638:5","text":"将 bxdf 连接到 output_collect"}
{"id":"9fd728c66c9a256b121472dabf32a34317aed01d8427d70ec830289cf23a7cc8","item_id":"19b5d27638:6","text":"添加"}
{"id":"4288ade73ff9d32824e931c858f11acab4e0a323e6b1da9bfbe124473a13ac5a","item_id":"19b5d27638:7","text":"Pattern"}
{"id":"aa37114c6e8721759fd39e5323dccbaf1e38d4b03bcea83ea20d8e1fa1ca7c62","item_id":"19b5d27638:8","text":"VOP 来修改 Bxdf 设置。下面我们把 PxrTexture 连接到 Diffuse Color。还会添加一个带纹理的 PxrDisplace 到 out_collect 上的第二个 shader slot。（如果使用置换，请确保你的对象设置了非零 displacement bound）"}
{"id":"e81d988bb3e766fcfc9128f1579f2d5eb6745618e9ced83e3740d29ac4b7803e","item_id":"19b5d27638:9","text":"Assign Material（分配 Material）"}
{"id":"d5b504f6f143e06342e19a4415b69eece6302f74fb2d7ce4a27d0e63aeae6c08","item_id":"19b5d27638:10","text":"要把材质分配给对象，只需将 material op path 拖到 Material。"}
